parameters: Shop Clerk: Thank you very much~!!
00_st_akane02_nomal
Akane: Phew~...!!

Akane: Finally, I was able to do some satisfying shopping.
It's been a while since I've indulged like this, I'm looking
forward to tonight's dinner!
Reisha: Ah, indeed...
00_st_akane02_shyness

Akane: Hey, how long are you going to keep worrying about
it?

Reisha: It's impossible not to worry... after what
happened...
00_st_akane02_smile

Akane: Hahaha! Well, let this be a lesson to spend a little
less frivolously, Sir Knight♪

Reisha: That's true. And from now on, let's find separate
ways to earn our travel funds. I feel like our common sense
doesn't quite align.
00_st_akane02_nomal
Akane: That's my line, seriously...
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: But man, I'm jealous. If only I had a splendid body
like yours...

Akane: When in trouble, just a little flirtation with the
guys around and I wouldn't have to worry about going hungry.
00_st_akane02_smile
Akane: Well, whatever. Let's hurry on with our journey!!
00_st_akane02_nomal
Akane: Huh, what's that?
Reisha: Hey! Take a look at this, Akane!

Reisha: Can you believe this spear? The shopkeeper's late
grandfather got it from a friend who was a renowned arms
dealer...!! They say the spearhead strikes like lightning
and leaves dragon claw marks on the battlefield when
swung...!

Reisha: Moreover, if you buy it now, it comes with a pot
holder, a fruit knife, a hand-knitted sweater, and even a
special pillow as part of a time sale...!! This is amazing!!

Reisha: We have some spare change right now! You want it
too, don't you Akane!!
00_st_akane02_serious

Akane: Retraction of previous statement. I'd rather stay
small than have my head filled with the naivety of a
sheltered life like yours...!
Reisha: Hm? Akane, did you say something?
00_st_akane02_smile
(What's this, she can be quite cute when she smiles...!)
00_st_akane02_nomal
Akane: Nothing~?? Come on, let's get going!
